{
  "name": "Wand of Lightning Bolts",
  "type": "consumable",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">(Requires attunement by a spellcaster)</em></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.IyikgTEOTv701jgQ]{Lightning Bolt} spell (save DC 15) from it. For 1 charge, you cast the 3rd-level version of the spell. You can increase the spell slot level by one for each additional charge you expend.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">The wand regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.</p>",
